{"tid":256067,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳方安生搞2047研討會  香港前途議程開始","createTime":"2017-05-24T09:20:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T03:42:49.000Z","uid":38671,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9109a137f7de50ead322ceae016bd302be847085","tid":256067,"uid":38671,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T09:20:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170524/large/1495615838_1b33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170524%2Flarge%2F1495615838_1b33.jpg&h=7968c5bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前政務司司長陳方安生、今日與公民實踐基金董事、吳明欽女兒吳思諾會見記者，宣佈將會舉行研討會，討論「2047：香港何去何從？」。陳太指如基本法20年來覆行得好，能保障原來人權自由，港人不會特別關心2047年後情況，因為知道香港能繼續貢獻國家，但現實是一國兩制過去20年不斷變質變形，令港人擔心未到2047年，香港已變成一國一制，年輕人亦擔心能否保持生活方式，由於一國兩制處於如此地步，因此要討論香港2047後如何繼續扮演獨特角色。<br />\n<br />\n陳太指，香港過去廿年發生銅鑼灣書店事件、人大釋法、議員被取消資格、打擊學術自由，加上3月特首選舉，中聯辦不掩飾粗暴干預等事件，都令港人非常關注2047年後仍會否有一國兩制和高度自治，投資者亦擔心地契屆時如何處理，法庭是否仍有司法獨立等，故目前討論是合時宜，希望巿民踴躍參加論壇。"},{"pid":"3b65e519b6952b499cf6c1f5a9c659ec01926afc","tid":256067,"uid":50616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T09:22:27.000Z","msg":"其實陳方安生係唔係「中共大中華膠」？"},{"pid":"84de67c6d447903284283148833ac20bc95b3a64","tid":256067,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T09:22:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170524/56736396\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170524%2F56736396&d=K6Hxr2sAvescS5eMpjBEQMmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=8c3258e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170524%2F56736396&h=bf886b0b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170524/56736396</a><br />\n<br />\n本土派港獨派應該去<br />\n唔好由得班老人繼續講廢話"},{"pid":"656cca9559ea8d6a657ad46856280dde698d7391","tid":256067,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T09:32:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實陳方安生係唔係「中共大中華膠」？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMartin果個friend"},{"pid":"04f1d8b65fa2d63578eb94c62179a75b3cf95605","tid":256067,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T03:11:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5f3cabaa49df300a77cb81f8a24d276dd5bc7f71","tid":256067,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T03:42:49.000Z","msg":"HKVDC_2017唔好掛住叫大陸雞呀"}]}